PVC Plastic Hardcover Design: The waterproof round-cornered hardcover is made of PVC plastic, which not only prevents the inner paper getting damaged, but also stiff enough to allows you to draw or write when you are standing.

Great use: AHGXG spiral lined notebooks are great for writing, work, school, office, home and travel. The spiral notebooks make a thoughtful and practical gift for anyone who loves to write, note-taking or stay organized, including, students, friends, family, and colleagues.

Waterproof PVC Cover PVC cover is water-resistant, oil-resistant, and fold-resistant, making the notebook durable and long-lasting. Divider Sticky Notes From color coding your documents to bookmarking important pages, these sticky notes will get you organized. And you can quickly and easily go back and retrieve information. Sturdy Wirebound Design The wire rings are sturdy and big enough to hold a pen. 180° Lay Flat Flexible Twin-Wire binding allowing the notebook to lay flat, flip and fold over on itself for maximum comfort and flexibility. Safety Round Corner Design Humanized and safe rounded corner design will not hurt children. 100GSM Premium Paper The archival-quality pages made from acid-free paper, which means it resists damage from light and air, ensuring long-lasting, and perfect to write and draw on, suit for most pens.

Are these college ruled or wide ruled？How many lines per page? Classic College Ruled, 7mm line spacing. 300 pages/150 sheets (1 sheet = 2 pages) A4: 36 lines each page, A5: 26 lines each page, B5: 32 lines each page. How about the binding of the notebook? Is it lay-flat when opened? We use flexible Twin-Wire binding allowing the notebook to 180° lay flat, flip and fold over. What is cover made of? PVC plastic hardcover, which is water-resistant, oil-resistant, and fold-resistant, making the notebook durable and long-lasting.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars VERY NICE - NONE BETTER (Yet!)
reviews.reviewText: A) Cover is a smooth, flexible, easy to clean - a contemporaryLake Blue (or, call it "Tiffany Blue" if you wear your diamond necklaces daily!😎)Also,B) Cover is also clean in appearance (no distracting company logos, barcodes, or other advertising);C) Pale-creme pages (AND: MANY OF THEM!!!) are easily turnedD) College ruled; Horizontal lines are appearing as discrete gray DOTSacross the width of the pages: (providing structure but NOT impeding easy legibility of notations);E) A thick, sturdy 8/5" x 11" booklet, excellent fornote taking @ lecture halls;daily personal journal/diary entries;orcomposing poetry /short stories.I ❤ it for daily recording of expenses / budgeting.!!!🤓AN APPEALING PRODUCT @ GREAT VALUE👍👍

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for my work needs!
reviews.reviewText: I need to take a lot of notes for work, so I can go through notebooks quickly. The number of college-ruled pages caught my attention. I was worried the pages might bleed ink for fine tipped pens, but they handle them and highlighters without any bleed at all. The lack of sections also makes it easier to flip through (these can be distracting for me), but if I need visual callouts, the book comes with sticky flags. Excellent for note-takers!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good but not perfect
reviews.reviewText: Has everything you need. Very good quality. Would've been perfect if the pages would've had holes and perforation for removing and filing separately in a college binder.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Large size, date bracket at the top of each lined page.Easy to return to personal diary item , by date.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Handy size notebook
reviews.reviewText: Convenient sized notebook. Like the date line at top of every page which reminds me to date and track my notes. Also appreciate the spiral binding making access to every page easy and smooth.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is the biggest notebook I’ve ever seen in my entire life. Like superDEdooper big! I’m blind on a good day, so having something for work this huge is very accommodating for office productivity. Definitely recommend this notebook if you like BIG ones!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Notebook for Writing.
reviews.reviewText: As an aspiring writer, I’m always looking for a really good notebook. I can say with certainty I found the right notebook. I can’t wait to a few more to help me write The Royal Series.
